Class AbstractDS_Aggregate_Type

Namespace
NDSH.Geospatial.Metadata.Application
Assembly
NDSH.Geospatial.Metadata.ISO19115.Ed2003.dll

Represents an identifiable collection of datasets in the ISO 19115 metadata standard. This abstract class serves as a base type for various dataset aggregations.

[IsoType("AbstractDS_Aggregate_Type", IsoType = IsoTypes.ComplexType)]
[JsonObject("AbstractDS_Aggregate")]
public abstract class AbstractDS_Aggregate_Type : MetadataObject, IModel, IObservableModel, INotifyPropertyChanged, IDbId, IObjectIdentification, INullableId, INullableUuid, ITypeReferenced
